      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it doesn't matter how much people care or how many \"steps\" i take. there's just nothing left to step on. the hole is too deep. i feel like i'm already gone, like i've already reached the end of my life and i'm just waiting for my body to realize it. everything is just empty now.",
